    <description>Plants to 35 m, usually less than 20 m. Winter buds pubescent, hairs relatively
        short, stiff. Leaves: blade base with 0 basilaminar glands, apex short-acuminate, abaxial
        surface glabrous at emergence; preformed blade with (3–)5–10 teeth on each side; neoformed
        blade lengths usually less than widths. Pedicels: lengths uniform, (5–)8–12(–15 in fruit)
        mm. Capsules with thick, stiff valves.</description>
